title: Tensorflow model as executable file
body_html:
I want to share my model as an executable file (without sharing my source code ) . I am using Tensorflow on Ubutun 16.04.1 LTS .I tried pyinstaller and cx_freeze but it give me alot of errors

pyinstaller error

cx_freeze error

I installed pyqt4 and I got this error
Error loading Python lib '/root/build/test/libpython2.7.so.1.0': /root/build/test/libpython2.7.so.1.0: cannot open shared object file: No such file or directory
